node.text:
7 months ago I was pulled out of this river by police and told I wasn’t allowed to clean up the river.. uploaded the video and you guys were upset.. well your voice was heard LOUD AND CLEAR since then we have teamed up with the entire city on San Antonio and they hooked us up with a boat, captain, and shut down the river for two days to allow me to dive and clean up. Seriously was an unreal opportunity and I’m so so grateful for everyone involved.👊🏼💙 also... this is a true testimony to just how strong and powerful you guys are. So dang lucky to have your support 💪🏼🔥

The first of a two video series is live on the YouTube channel!! 

📸- @manticore.media 

#iloveyousanantonio #riverwalk #treasure #underwater
